# - Try to find MOAB
# Once done this will define
#
#  MOAB_FOUND - system has MOAB
#  MOAB_INCLUDE_DIRS - the MOAB include directory
#  MOAB_LIBRARIES - Link these to use MOAB
#  MOAB_DEFINITIONS - Compiler switches required for using MOAB
